39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe8f7cdd072c64d262644728c38e0baf9bd9842","tid":2502862,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbc5b845cfee1530fec71bddb23868084cf15f6d","tid":2502862,"uid":20272,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"由2017年到今年年頭我都同好多人一樣對RE7完全無興趣, <br />\n原因都係第一身+無喪屍敵人又少+劇情同本身RE故事關係極細<br />\n講緊係我已經上網睇過哂人打都覺得隻game 麻麻<br />\n<br />\n然後見PS5免費, 自己親身打完<br />\n發覺佢真係比起正傳4,5,6, 甚至RE2R, RE3R 更有資格稱得上survival horror game<br />\n成個map/ 幾個area既地理設計/鋪排, Inventory management 既平衡度都係一流<br />\n而且以一個新故事令玩家失去哂因為對RE故事既熟悉而免疫既能力<br />\n真係一流既horror game<br />\n<br />\n舉個例, 雖然Jack Baker追住玩家既時間唔多, <br />\n但佢所帶黎既壓迫感, 出現既鋪排, 都比起RE2R/ RE3R 既Mr.X/ Nemesis更強<br />\n起碼你見到佢, 好多時真係要硬食兩野, 唔似可以避 Mr.X/ Nemesis果種情況<br />\n<br />\n依幾日見到RE8 有Lady Dimitrescu 追住Ethan 啲gameplay, 有少少擔心好似Mr.X咁單一"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"其實7一向評價都唔錯，啲人最多係屌佢唔似傳統bio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係本身隻驚係高汁"},{"pid":"9144773319d14b17587ef1d99f4fecaceff453b9","tid":2502862,"uid":218407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"頭先玩ps4 30min demo暈撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇清知道點樣可以減低3d暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306a5cfd7ca7fbb67f768e4de4d796ae225506b0","tid":2502862,"uid":263534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9144773319d14b17587ef1d99f4fecaceff453b9","tid":2502862,"uid":218407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"頭先玩ps4 30min demo暈撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇清知道點樣可以減低3d暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"試下較光啲，太暗要專注望清楚好易暈"},{"pid":"208a7d952292fe6e74cce860be3e4f16be1e0eed","tid":2502862,"ui