oji\" /><br />\n有冇清知道點樣可以減低3d暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"太低Fps都會暈"},{"pid":"a4fbd1ca51ce509915c611d05439c359b90a44c7","tid":2502862,"uid":634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T17:38:53.000Z","msg":"希望流程長d、boss戰多d、難度高d <br />\n7無乜挑戰 流程太短 瘋人院難度又唔難打"},{"pid":"a12c810c4de0cdae8f4209626f3b80f62e91d810","tid":2502862,"uid":7916,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2fe8f7cdd072c64d262644728c38e0baf9bd9842","tid":2502862,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbc5b845cfee1530fec71bddb23868084cf15f6d","tid":2502862,"uid":20272,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"由2017年到今年年頭我都同好多人一樣對RE7完全無興趣, <br />\n原因都係第一身+無喪屍敵人又少+劇情同本身RE故事關係極細<br />\n講緊係我已經上網睇過哂人打都覺得隻game 麻麻<br />\n<br />\n然後見PS5免費, 自己親身打完<br />\n發覺佢真係比起正傳4,5,6, 甚至RE2R, RE3R 更有資格稱得上survival horror game<br />\n成個map/ 幾個area既地理設計/鋪排, Inventory management 既平衡度都係一流<br />\n而且以一個新故事令玩家失去哂因為對RE故事既熟悉而免疫既能力<br />\n真係一流既horror game<br />\n<br />\n舉個例, 雖然Jack Baker追住玩家既時間唔多, <br />\n但佢所帶黎既壓迫感, 出現既鋪排, 都比起RE2R/ RE3R 既Mr.X/ Nemesis更強<br />\n起碼你見到佢, 好多時真係要硬食兩野, 唔似可以避 Mr.X/ Nemesis果種情況<br />\n<br />\n依幾日見到RE8 有Lady Dimitrescu 追住Ethan 啲gameplay, 有少少擔心好似Mr.X咁單一"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"其實7一向評價都唔錯，啲人最多係屌佢唔似傳統bio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係本身隻驚係高汁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"啲人講傳統真係哂鳩氣 由得4開始已經偏離咗傳統啦 傳統係fixed camera angle添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a01776ef3cc161a6e27d43d1ff78d3854d7746d","tid":2502862,"uid":38997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a12c810c4de0cdae8f4209626f3b80f62e91d810","tid":2502862,"uid":7916,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2fe8f7cdd072c64d262644728c38e0baf9bd9842","tid":2502862,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"