RE2R/ RE3R 既Mr.X/ Nemesis更強<br />\n起碼你見到佢, 好多時真係要硬食兩野, 唔似可以避 Mr.X/ Nemesis果種情況<br />\n<br />\n依幾日見到RE8 有Lady Dimitrescu 追住Ethan 啲gameplay, 有少少擔心好似Mr.X咁單一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"咁多隻RE，7係我心目中遠遠拋離其他同系列作品<br />\n<br />\n唯一不滿係自己廢，初初玩打到想嘔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b225ce49b79d1b24cf4e6f4266b09533a0bf26","tid":2502862,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7cfe308ec2abde8dbc0bcb3db16f0ee7ec4786b0","tid":2502862,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73969f0694215f13ebe8582dc5f31a1a636060b6","tid":2502862,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a60e11c2572a4053b2ae3b028faae00d41d97b","tid":2502862,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"流暢度不足<br />\n請玩pc/ps5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"Ps5都係得45fps"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"打漏左最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔開rt先可以鎖到60<br />\n但開左靚好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"有好多channel check過，兩個demo就算開RT, PS5 既fps好似最多都係跌到落around 53~55,而且只係間中唯持一兩秒果種<br />\n<br />\n基本上PS5 就算開RT 都長時間keep到60fps"},{"pid":"0e3fb2ae9fbf850d830d9a3044b7c4aff0b70578","tid":2502862,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"想俾Miranda踩J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f7e3a9039e37f7386f0b64a68934f05d916810","tid":2502862,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e3fb2ae9fbf850d830d9a3044b7c4aff0b70578","tid":2502862,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"想俾Miranda踩J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:21:57.000Z","msg"